articles.title: Hollywood strikes cast shadow over Venice film festival - Financial Times
articles.description: Annual event lacks many of its biggest names as others use it as a platform to attack streaming services
articles.content:
Actors have used the Venice film festival as a platform to attack streaming services as the annual jamboree proceeds without many of its biggest stars because of strikes in Hollywood.
